{"doc":{"isMarkdown":true,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"BatteryManager.chargingTime","mdn_url":"/fr/docs/Web/API/BatteryManager/chargingTime","locale":"fr","native":"Français","sidebarHTML":"<ol><li><strong><a href=\"/fr/docs/Web/API/Battery_Status_API\">Battery Status API</a></strong></li><li><strong><a href=\"/fr/docs/Web/API/BatteryManager\"><code>BatteryManager</code></a></strong></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Propriétés</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/fr/docs/Web/API/BatteryManager/charging\"><code>charging</code></a></li><li><em><code>chargingTime</code></em></li><li><a href=\"/fr/docs/Web/API/BatteryManager/dischargingTime\"><code>dischargingTime</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/fr/docs/Web/API/BatteryManager/level\"><code>level</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Événements</summary><ol><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/BatteryManager/chargingchange_event\"><code>chargingchange</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/BatteryManager/chargingtimechange_event\"><code>chargingtimechange</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/BatteryManager/dischargingtimechange_event\"><code>dischargingtimechange</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/BatteryManager/levelchange_event\"><code>levelchange</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Héritage&nbsp;:</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/fr/docs/Web/API/EventTarget\"><code>EventTarget</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Pages liées à Battery API</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/fr/docs/Web/API/Navigator/getBattery\"><code>Navigator.getBattery()</code></a></li></ol></details></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p>La propriété <strong><code>BatteryManager.chargingTime</code></strong> indique le temps, en secondes, qu'il reste jusqu'à que la batterie soit rechargée, ou vaut <code>0</code> si la batterie est déjà rechargée. Si la batterie est en décharge, la variable vaut <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Infinity\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">Infinity (en-US)</a>. Lorsque sa valeur change, l'évènement <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/BatteryManager/chargingtimechange_event\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">chargingtimechange (en-US)</a> est déclenché.</p>\n<div class=\"notecard note\" id=\"sect1\">\n  <p><strong>Note :</strong> Même si le temps retourné devrait être précis à la seconde, les navigateurs arrondissent cette valeur (typiquement à 15 minutes près) pour des raisons de confidentialité.</p>\n</div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"exemple","title":"Exemple","isH3":false,"content":""}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"html","title":"HTML","isH3":true,"content":"<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: html notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>div</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">id</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>chargingTime<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>(temps de charge inconnu)<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>div</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n</code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"